serializableData.oldContent: When playing in HADES mode the chance to hit the FREE SPINS feature is lower but the average win of FREE SPINS rounds is higher.
When playing in OLYMPUS mode the chance to hit the FREE SPINS feature is higher but the average win of FREE SPINS rounds is lower.
The FREE SPINS round can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it.
These are EXPANDING WILD symbols. They appear on all reels.
The theoretical RTP of this game when playing in HADES mode is {0}%
All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
Cost of 75x total bet will award a standard FREE SPINS feature.
Cost of 300x total bet will award a special FREE SPINS feature in which one expanding WILD is guaranteed to hit with a random multiplier and in a random position on the first free spin of the round.
The game has two profiles that can be chosen by the player, OLYMPUS and HADES modes. Depending on the profile chosen the look of the game changes to match the respective profile.
These are SCATTER symbols. They appear only on reels 1, 3 and 5 and only in the base game.
Free spins round total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.

The maximum win amount is limited to {0}x bet in both base game and free spins. If the total win of a FREE SPINS round reaches {1}x bet the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited
The multiplier applies to all winning combinations that it is part of. If more than one WILD is part of the same winning combination, their multipliers add to each other.
Only the highest win is paid per line.

All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines.
Free spins win is added to the payline win. 
All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
Special reels are in play during the feature.
Hit 3 SCATTER symbols to trigger the FREE SPINS feature and get 10 free spins.
Cost of 300x total bet will award a special FREE SPINS feature in which one expanding WILD is guaranteed to hit with a random multiplier and in a random position on the first free spin of the round.

During the round any expanding WILD symbol that hits will expand, get a random multiplier from the same possible values as in the base game and will remain on the screen until the end of the round, for all free spins.
Free spins round win is awarded to the player after the round completes.

All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.

Whenever any of them hits in the base game or FREE SPINS, if there would be any win after expansion, it expands the whole reel vertically and get a random multiplier. Possible values are 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 7x, 8x, 9x, 10x, 20x, 25x, 50x or 100x.

SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.

serializableData._text: Spljot HADES rem, iespja uzgriezt BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildspli ir mazka, bet vidjais BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU raundu laimests ir lielks.
Spljot OLYMPUS rem, iespja uzgriezt BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildspli ir augstka, bet vidjais BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU raundu laimests ir mazks.
BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU raundu var uzskt pamatsples laik, noprkot to.
ie ir AUGOIE WILD simboli. Tie ir uzgrieami uz vism spolm.
Spltja teortisk iespja laimt (RTP) HADES rem ir {0}%
Laimestu maks par simboliem no kreiss puses uz labo, skot no kreiss malas uz blakus esom spolm.
Darbbas traucjumi anul visas izmaksas un sples.
Par 75x kopjo likmi tiks pieirta BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildsple.
Par 300x kopjo likmi tiks pieirta pa BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildsple, kur tiek garantta augoo WILD simbolu uzgrieana ar nejauu reizintju un nejau pozcij pirm raunda bezmaksas grieziena laik.
aj spl spltja izvlei ir pieejami divi profili OLYMPUS un HADES remi. Atkarb no izvlt profila, sples izskats mains atbilstoi attiecgajam profilam.
ie ir SCATTER simboli. Tie pards tikai uz 1., 3. un 5. spoles, bet tikai pamatspl.
Bezmaksas griezienu laimestu vstur tiek iekauta visa cikla kopj laimesta summa.

Maksiml laimesta summa ir ierobeota ldz {0}x likmei gan pamatspl, gan bezmaksas griezienu papildspl. Ja kopj BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU RAUNDA kopj laimesta summa sasniedz {1}x likmi, raunds nekavjoties beidzas, laimests tiek pieirts un visi atlikuie bezmaksas griezieni tiek atcelti.
Reizintjs tiek piemrots vism laimestu kombincijm, kurs tas piedals. Ja vienu laimjoo kombinciju veido vairki WILD simboli, tad to reizintji tiek reizinti saskaitti kop.

Laimestu izmaks par simboliem no kreiss puses uz labo izvltajs izmaksas lnijs.
Bezmaksas griezienu laimests tiek pievienots izmaksas rindas laimestam.
Visi laimesti tiek reizinti ar likmi katr rind.
Papildsples laik tiek izmantotas pas spoles.
Uzgriez 3 SCATTER simbolus, lai aktiviztu BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildspli un iegtu 10 bezmaksas griezienus.
Par 300x kopjo likmi tiks pieirta pa BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildsple, kur tiek garantta augoo WILD simbolu uzgrieana ar nejauu reizintju un nejau pozcij pirm raunda bezmaksas grieziena laik.
HADES rem ir pieejamas das pirkanas iespjas:
Spltja iespja laimt (RTP), izmantojot "PIRKT SUPER BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENUS" HADES rema laik ir {0}%
Laimjot vairks izmaksu rinds, visus laimestus pievieno kopjam laimestam.
OLYMPUS rem ir pieejamas das pirkanas iespjas:
is ir Wild simbols, kas aizstj visus citus simbolus izemot SCATTER.
Raunda laik jebkur augoais WILD Simbols, kas tiks uzgriezts, izpletsies, iegs nejauu reizintju no tm pam iespjamajm vrtbm k pamatspl un paliks uz ekrna ldz raunda beigm visu bezmaksas griezienu laik.
Bezmaksas griezieni tiek pieirti spltjam pc raunda beigm.
Spltja iespja laimt (RTP), izmantojot "PIRKT BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENUS" OLYMPUS rema laik ir {0}%

Par 150x kopjo likmi tiks pieirta BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildsple.
Spltja iespja laimt (RTP), izmantojot "PIRKT SUPER BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENUS" OLYMPUS rema laik ir {0}%

Katru reizi, kad kds no tiem tiek uzgriezts pamatsples vai BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU laik, ja pc paplainans btu laimests, tas izpleas vertikli pa visu spoli un iegst nejauu reizintju. Iespjams vrtbas ir 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 7x, 8x, 9x, 10x, 20x, 25x, 50x vai 100x.

ATSTARPES un ENTER taustius uz tastatras var izmantot, lai sktu un apturtu griezienu.
Augstas neparedzambas spls vidji izmaks laimestus retk, tau iespja gt lielus laimestus s laika sprd ir augstka.
